schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: Mountain charm meets Modern Convenience with the potential of taking over the current loan and obtaining a 3.25% interest rate!!! Newly built in 2020, this stunning home has lots to offer. Located in the beautiful neighborhood of Upper Running Springs with easy access to Highway 330, Lake Arrowhead, and Big Bear. Just a few steps up to the front porch and into spacious open-concept living. No other steps once you're inside as it's all one story. High ceilings with dual pane windows and quality window coverings throughout. The wood-burning stove is optimally placed to heat the entirety of the home. There is ample space for the dining room and bar top seating. An eye-catching, live edge red milled cedar bar top was sourced from the property during construction. The kitchen offers granite countertops and a generous amount of cabinetry. The various skylights in the home provide an abundance of natural light. The master bedroom provides a sizable walk-in closet and high ceilings. Head out the back door to the large backyard that is fully fenced and has the potential to make it your own. There's nothing better than having a full-size, fully insulated garage with direct entry into the home. Unique opportunity to own one of the newer builds in Running Springs.
